<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&display=swap');
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { width: 1200px; height: 630px; overflow: hidden; background: #0D0D0D; }
  .canvas {
    width: 1200px;
    height: 630px;
    background: #0D0D0D;
    position: relative;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(232,67,26,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,67,26,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .glow-left {
    position: absolute;
    left: -100px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,67,26,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .glow-right {
    position: absolute;
    right: -80px;
    bottom: -80px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,67,26,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .border-top {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #E8431A, #FF6B35, #E8431A, transparent);
  }
  .border-bottom {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #E8431A, #FF6B35, #E8431A, transparent);
  }
  .content {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 100px;
    gap: 60px;
  }
  .left {
    flex: 1;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(232,67,26,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,67,26,0.4);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .badge-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: #E8431A;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .badge-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #E8431A;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .brand {
    font-size: 88px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -3px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .brand span {
    color: #E8431A;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #E8431A;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .services {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .service-item {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .service-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    background: #E8431A;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .lobster {
    font-size: 130px;
    line-height: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(232,67,26,0.5));
  }
  .url-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    font-family: 'Syne', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .corner-tl, .corner-tr, .corner-bl, .corner-br {
    position: absolute;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }
  .corner-tl { top: 20px; left: 20px; border-top: 2px solid #E8431A; border-left: 2px solid #E8431A; }
  .corner-tr { top: 20px; right: 20px; border-top: 2px solid #E8431A; border-right: 2px solid #E8431A; }
  .corner-bl { bottom: 20px; left: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #E8431A; border-left: 2px solid #E8431A; }
  .corner-br { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #E8431A; border-right: 2px solid #E8431A; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="canvas">
  <div class="grid"></div>
  <div class="glow-left"></div>
  <div class="glow-right"></div>
  <div class="border-top"></div>
  <div class="border-bottom"></div>
  <div class="corner-tl"></div>
  <div class="corner-tr"></div>
  <div class="corner-bl"></div>
  <div class="corner-br"></div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="left">
      <div class="badge">
        <div class="badge-dot"></div>
        <span class="badge-text">AI Agent 專家</span>
      </div>
      <div class="brand">Think<br><span>BIG</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">Think Big! Make it Real.</div>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div class="services">
        <div class="service-item"><div class="service-dot"></div>龍蝦 AI Agent 安裝 &amp; 設定</div>
        <div class="service-item"><div class="service-dot"></div>企業 AI 自動化方案</div>
        <div class="service-item"><div class="service-dot"></div>客製化 AI 禮品 &amp; 3D 列印</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <div class="lobster">🦞</div>
      <div class="url-box">thinkbigtw.com</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
